    AbstractProcessor
    Provides functionality and attributes common to all supported protocols (currently HTTP and AJP).

  • 异常错误概要 
    异常错误 说明
    CloseNowException
    This exception is thrown to signal to the Tomcat internals that an error has occurred that requires the connection to be closed.
